                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d250">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Russell</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Bogotá</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1905-03-21">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 21, 1905</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Russell reports that the claim of the Compañia Fluvial de Cartagena et al.
                    against the Government of Colombia has been settled by that government by an
                    offer of $475,000 in bonds, which was accepted by the agent of the
                    companies.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
